PlotRemote - auto_plot 中的 接口
The PlotRemote class provides a Java RMI-compliant interface to the M-functions from the files: G:\\Program Files\\MATLAB\\R2011a\\bin\\draw_curve_auto.m The dispose() method must be called on a PlotRemote instance when it is no longer needed to ensure that native resources allocated by this class are properly freed, and the server-side proxy is unexported.
